data.description: Quite and serene Lake Community, just across from open water. Property sets high on a hill overlooking the water across the street. Great views from the upstairs Bedroom Balcony. This 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home features a Large master suite down stairs. The family room opens to the front of the home stepping out on a large deck area. Lots of trees to shade the summer sun. Laundry room will accommodate full size appliances, also lots of shelving in the Laundry room. Great for full time residents or a weekend get a way.  Community offers Boat Launch, Pool, Picnic area, Tennis court, and Basketball Goals.
